OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Finflation, warns John Lewis
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, An exodus of over-50s who left the     
OL,6, workforce during the Covid pandemic is 
OL,7, fuelling wage inflation, says the boss 
OL,8, of John Lewis.                         
OL,10,FDame Sharon White said any government  
OL,11,Fmust think "really hard" about how to  
OL,12,Fget more older people back into work.  
OL,14,FThe UK has seen one million people,    
OL,15,Fmostly in their 50s, leave work since  
OL,16,Fthe start of the Covid-19 outbreak.    
OL,18,FThat "inevitably" causes wage          
OL,19,Finflation, said Dame Sharon.           
